# No Inline Styles

- Do not use inline style objects in JSX (`style={{ ... }}`).
- Do not set styles via direct DOM style mutations in components.
- Prefer:
  - Component-level `styles` files
  - CSS modules
  - Shared theme/tokens from the design system

## Examples

```tsx
// BAD
<div style={{ marginTop: 16, color: '#111' }} />

// GOOD
<div className="profileCard" />
```
